  "body": "Similarly to #2970 I think `msg.gas` is very misleading as it seems to suggest the gaslimit for that given message, which is immutable, but rather it is a mutable gas left property.\r\n\r\nI'd argue it makes more sense making it a global function named `gasleft()` (alternatively `gasleft` as a property similar to `<address>.balance`).",
